### One Fix Applied

**`apps/desktop/src/styles/workspace.css` — orphaned CSS declaration** (origin: sf5-104 builder)

Builder sf5-104 left a bare `overflow: auto;` declaration outside any selector block, preceded by a stray section comment. This caused two esbuild CSS minification warnings during production build (`Expected identifier` / `Unexpected ";"`). The declaration was not inside any rule so had no effect on styling. **Removed** the orphaned line and its comment — the correctly-scoped multi-select inspector rules immediately following it are preserved intact.

